<p>第三方支付已经彻底融入了人们的生产和生活中了，它一定会出现下面这样的场景。</p>
<figure><img src="https://tianmazuo.com/technology/programming/java/thread-07.png" alt="循环等待" tabindex="0" loading="lazy"><figcaption>循环等待</figcaption></figure>
